{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id7945c23b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"720"},"text":"§ 720.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this chapter:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c23c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Alaska natural gas","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “Alaska natural gas” means natural gas derived from the area of the State of Alaska lying north of 64 degrees north latitude.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c23d-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Alaska natural gas transportation project","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The term “Alaska natural gas transportation project” means any natural gas pipeline system that carries Alaska natural gas to the border between Alaska and Canada (including related facilities subject to the jurisdiction of the Commission) that is authorized under—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c23e-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the Alaska Natural Gas Transportation Act of 1976 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s719"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 719","children":[],"tail":" et seq.); or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c23f-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s720a"},"text":"section 720a of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c240-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Alaska natural gas transportation system","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “Alaska natural gas transportation system” means the Alaska natural gas transportation project authorized under the Alaska Natural Gas Transportation Act of 1976 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s719"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 719","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) and designated and described in section 2 of the President’s decision."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c241-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Commission","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “Commission” means the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7945c242-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s720/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading",